content.title: Step 3: Package Your Lambda Function
content.visibleText:
simple_salesforce

Step 3: Package Your Lambda Function

1. Deactivate the Virtual Environment:

bash
deactivate

2. Create a Deployment Package:

bash
cd venv/lib/python3.x/site-packages/ # replace 'python3.x' with your Python version
zip -r9 ${OLDPWD}/function.zip .
cd $OLDPWD
zip -g function.zip lambda_function.
